title: Tuesday Post Show (10-19-21)
itunes:title: Tuesday Post Show (10-19-21)
description:
Bobby starts by apologizing to Eddie for not bringing him muffins. He also talks about how the top app people are deleting Facebook. We also try to solve Amy’s missing cookie dilemma. We also update on the winner of the Superhero draft. Eddie wants to know if anyone got an email from his son because he found him on his computer. Bobby also shares an unfortunate story of when he invited the wrong “Clark” to his house. He was trying to invite another guy he worked with who happened to be named “Clark”. Amy also gives us an update on her daughter making the box of WNBA goals and how much she made for it.
